{"id": "1432523386034323577", "channel_id": "1432523386034323577", "type": 0, "author_id": "954133451810947123", "author_name": "osseinn", "author_bot": false, "content": "I know im fairly new and havent really gotten deep into the game, ive pulled a bit for characters and strongly believe that I want to build a Caro team, the whole playstyle is cool to me. I have recently gotten my hands on these \"Protoparadise\" things and my question is: Who should I be getting to help fuel my Caro team for story and future endeavors?", "timestamp": "2025-10-28T00:16:30.228000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1432523386528993320", "filename": "Screenshot_2025-10-27_201205.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1417220, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1432523386034323577/1432523386528993320/Screenshot_2025-10-27_201205.png?ex=69cd0c9e&is=69cbbb1e&hm=233822fa917f40f937124b73b7254e5bce20b72a75ccc0e76c2b62820e9060e0&"}, {"id": "1432523387380699237", "filename": "Screenshot_2025-10-27_201408.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1887696, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1432523386034323577/1432523387380699237/Screenshot_2025-10-27_201408.png?ex=69cd0c9e&is=69cbbb1e&hm=5e41d291bb591299c1711ca330eb6c17cfa2a717f33897c5f1105626fb2fd21a&"}, {"id": "1432523387737079828", "filename": "Screenshot_2025-10-27_201438.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 407269, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1432523386034323577/1432523387737079828/Screenshot_2025-10-27_201438.png?ex=69cd0c9e&is=69cbbb1e&hm=6873047b225a18456b1acab4b843c462645ac47566006042ed196d6eb1796802&"}, {"id": "1432523388122824725", "filename": "Screenshot_2025-10-27_201522.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 293131, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1432523386034323577/1432523388122824725/Screenshot_2025-10-27_201522.png?ex=69cd0c9e&is=69cbbb1e&hm=66b9544c4d0665eec01c89fb29106fcf44debe21