{"id": "1432542701420679331", "channel_id": "1432523386034323577", "type": 0, "author_id": "513647413584592896", "author_name": "methanehydrate", "author_bot": false, "content": "Thais is the main support for Caro teams. For DPS there's many good options such as Salv, Gelot, or Doresain.", "timestamp": "2025-10-28T01:33:15.375000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1432523386034323577", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Need Team advice", "forum_channel_id": "1356200968311803956", "thread_tags": ["1400747489132412979", "1400747307745415228", "1400747088995811358"]}
{"id": "1432543211687247992", "channel_id": "1432523386034323577", "type": 19, "author_id": "954133451810947123", "author_name": "osseinn", "author_bot": false, "content": "Ive looked as some teams online, ive seen some people use winkle in their builds, do you know why?", "timestamp": "2025-10-28T01:35:17.032000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["513647413584592896"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1432542701420679331", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1432523386034323577", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Need Team advice", "forum_channel_id": "1356200968311803956", "thread_tags": ["1400747489132412979", "1400747307745415228", "1400747088995811358"]}
{"id": "1432613085549563976", "channel_id": "1432523386034323577", "type": 0, "author_id": "455376494034812948", "author_name": "reverie.is.dead", "author_bot": false, "content": "winkle's ult (exhalt) can generate aliemus for another team member, and at e3 she can allow that team member to ult twice in one turn. So if you're running someone who wants to ult a lot, she can be handy.", "timestamp": "2025-10-28T06:12:56.259000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1432523386034323577", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Need Team advice", "forum_channel_id": "1356200968311803956", "thread_tags": ["1400747489132412979", "1400747307745415228", "1400747088995811358"]}
{"id": "1432627720512208906", "channel_id": "1432523386034323577", "type": 19, "author_id": "1177477727029301321", "author_name": "a3th3r_69708", "author_bot": false, "content": "As a person that plays a LOT of caro. PULL THIAS. Shes by far the best unit in the realm to carry early accounts. Her battery is unmatched, her wheel is the best in the game and with thias + any caro dps, u can clear a lot of early game content (up to level 40, zero investment). Aigis is a caro unit u get for free, shes very good with thias. The comp I rec for u currently uvhash, faint/aigis, thias, remona. Highly rec also to invest in thias e2. gelot requires more investment for a newbie.", "timestamp": "2025-10-28T07:11:05.506000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["954133451810947123"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1432523386034323577", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1432523386034323577", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Need Team advice", "forum_channel_id": "1356200968311803956", "thread_tags": ["1400747489132412979", "1400747307745415228", "1400747088995811358"]}
