{"id": "1432629000219656203", "channel_id": "1431952789180776568", "type": 19, "author_id": "1177477727029301321", "author_name": "a3th3r_69708", "author_bot": false, "content": "tinct gimmicky af, dont rec her, but otherwise u could use faint, jenkins, daff, flex. Jenkins is great with daff, and faint needs a tad of investment to be good. Otherwise if u want to go for a doresain investment, i highly rec u also go for pickman as well", "timestamp": "2025-10-28T07:16:10.612000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["936687729528426577"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1431952789180776568", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1431952789180776568", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "how to build a good team w my units? who to pull for?", "forum_channel_id": "1356200968311803956", "thread_tags": ["1400747489132412979", "1400747333490184292", "1400747088995811358"]}
{"id": "1432570855405387897", "channel_id": "1432570855405387897", "type": 0, "author_id": "228903327591563264", "author_name": "capnkarlos", "author_bot": false, "content": "So, still new. In chapter 1 still, and after the beginner banner gave me Sanga, then all the other rolls given to us gave my multiple copies of her and some others.\n\nGoing forward, I assume I am building around Sanga. Any particular units to keep on the lookout for? I have the holy Flare's spreadsheet, and see that Castor is on banner and he's in the same archetype. Worth trying to get him or hold onto my pulls for someone else?", "timestamp": "2025-10-28T03:25:07.808000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1432570855921156238", "filename": "305BDA03-51B1-4FC9-8D3C-98659BE9C48A.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 2426199, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1432570855405387897/1432570855921156238/305BDA03-51B1-4FC9-8D3C-98659BE9C48A.png?ex=69cc9013&is=69cb3e93&hm=78238a87582db1bf0bcba8510bb3d4c5cad787ee10b454b5729c6f2dc60b5450&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1432570855405387897", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Team advice/character priority", "forum_channel_id": "1356200968311803956", "thread_tags": ["1400747088995811358"]}
{"id": "1432621850248351847", "channel_id": "1432570855405387897", "type": 0, "author_id": "455376494034812948", "author_name": "reverie.is.dead", "author_bot": false, "content": "Uh... castor himself is a viable hypercarry (i think dps at e3, good shielder at lower copies) so putting him on the same team as sanga might outshine her.... Maybe play his trial and see if you like how he works— if you like, pull, don't like then wait for a future banner (anniv gmurphy is soon, tawil rerun is soon etc) \n\nE0 castor can't hurt, but more important than castor E0 is probably 1 copy of castor's wheel since it's one of the few +2 handsize wheels.\n\nAs for sanga... you can safely continue to use standard pulls on blue realm until e3 caecus (reassess if you wanna keep pulling blue for sanga at that point), since sanga wants OE (i.e. E3+4 so original+7 extra copies) later on. Her OE (enhanced ult) is her key mechanism, so a support could be winkle (purple standards, her ult generates ult charge for a teammate, at e3 also lets them double ult). Compatible limiteds whose reruns you might wanna look out for are... horla (purple, joy stance increases ult charge gain for team) or miryam (blue, should have ritual cards that give ult charge). But you could make sanga work with other options too— murphy, caecus... esp at earlier chapters, almost anyone is fine.\n\nNote that you don't have to main sanga just because you pulled a lot of her. A reset pyramid probably comes soon-ish and you can swap her copies for other standards of ur choice.\n\n(I'm *not* a sanga expert so take this all with a grain of salt)", "timestamp": "2025-10-28T06:47:45.926000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1432570855405387897", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Team advice/character priority", "forum_channel_id": "1356200968311803956", "thread_tags": ["1400747088995811358"]}
{"id": "1432625740859310202", "channel_id": "1432570855405387897", "type": 0, "author_id": "1177477727029301321", "author_name": "a3th3r_69708", "author_bot": false, "content": "i highly rec just pulling castor + his wheel as both are very strong. Castor is great shielder at low e and dps at e3+.", "timestamp": "2025-10-28T07:03:13.520000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1432570855405387897", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Team advice/character priority", "forum_channel_id": "1356200968311803956", "thread_tags": ["1400747088995811358"]}
